          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C60A1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">A</hi> Bard, grown desirous of saving his Pelf,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C60A1-line-2" n="2">Built a little House he was sure would hold none but himself:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C60A1-line-3" n="3">This enraged <hi rend="italics">Apollo</hi>, who <hi rend="italics">Mercury</hi> sent,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C60A1-line-4" n="4">And bid him go ask, what his Votary meant.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C60A1-line-5" n="5">Some Foe to my Godship has been his Adviser;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C60A1-line-6" n="6">'Tis a dreadful Portent, when a Poet turns Miser:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C60A1-line-7" n="7">Tell him, <hi rend="italics">Hermes</hi>, from me, tell that Subject of mine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C60A1-line-8" n="8">I have sworn by the <hi rend="italics">Styx</hi> to defeat his Design;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C60A1-line-9" n="9">For, wherever he comes, the Muses shall reign;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C60A1-line-10" n="10">And the Muses, he knows, have a numerous Train.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
